These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, tea
House: gothic-revival, colonial
1. the gothic-revival house is in an even position##4
2. the colonial house is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Beverage   | tea | water |
| House     | colonial    | gothic-revival   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, january
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, folk
1. the fan of ambient is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Birthday   | january | june        |
| Music-Genre      | ambient  | folk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
City: paris, boston
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, swimming
1. the person who's sport is sailing is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| City   | boston    | paris |
| Sport   | sailing | swimming |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
2 different pets are kept: fish, rat
The people have 2 different jobs:  nurse, dressmaker
1. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
2. the dressmaker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Pet   | fish      | rat |
| Job       | nurse | dressmaker    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
