The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: family, time-travel
1. the person watching time-travel movies is the person who's sport is baseball##1
2. the person watching family movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |     2     |
| Sport          | baseball | surfing |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | family   |

